lead_paragraph: French driver Esteban Ocon will race for Force India next season after agreeing a multi-year deal, the Silverstone-based Formula One team said in a statement at the Brazilian Grand Prix on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Ocon Joins Force India F1 Team on Multi-Year Deal
